hummingbird (Java BC-UR implementation)
Copyright (c) 2020-2024 Sparrow Wallet
Licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0
https://github.com/sparrowwallet/hummingbird

The FountainDecoder, URDecoder, and related fountain code decoding logic
were ported from Java to Kotlin from this project. Modifications include
conversion to pure Kotlin with no external dependencies, removal of the
cbor-java dependency in favor of manual CBOR encoding/decoding, and
adaptation for Kotlin Multiplatform compatibility.

---

kotlin-hardware-wallet (Kotlin BC-UR implementation)
Copyright (c) 2024 iml1s
Licensed under the MIT License
https://github.com/iml1s/kotlin-hardware-wallet

The UREncoder, FountainEncoder, Bytewords, CRC32, SHA256, and
Xoshiro256StarStar implementations were derived from this project.
Modifications include package renaming, addition of CBOR decoding
(fromCborBytes), corrections to RandomSampler for cross-implementation
compatibility, and addition of the Xoshiro256StarStar string constructor
and nextData method.

